  "title": "audit assistant",
  "description": "<p>Assist in internal audit and review of financial records, including student fee collections, receipts, and payment vouchers</p><p>Perform checking and reconciliation of accounts, invoices, and supporting documents</p><p>Assist in reviewing internal controls and identifying discrepancies or areas for improvement</p><p>Support accounting reviews related to payroll, commissions, and expense claims</p><p>Prepare audit schedules, summaries, and basic reports for management review</p><p>Liaise with internal staff and the accountant remotely to verify information when required</p><p>Assist with ad-hoc finance, audit, and compliance-related tasks</p><p>Diploma or Bachelor’s degree in Accounting, Finance, or a related field</p><p>Basic understanding of accounting and auditing principles</p><p>Proficient in Microsoft Excel and Google Sheets</p><p>Detail-oriented, responsible, and able to handle confidential information</p><p>Able to work independently and meet deadlines in a remote working environment</p><p>Part-time or Full-time position with flexible working hours</p><p>Work-from-home arrangement; occasional on-site attendance may be required (if necessary)</p>",
